* Avoid $_SERVER["PHP_SELF"] Exploits.
<form method="post" action="<?php echo htmlspecialchars($_SERVER["PHP_SELF"]);?>">

* Database.
** Password hash: $secure_pass = password_hash($pass, PASSWORD_BCRYPT);


